        public java.util.List<Pair<IEntityType,java.util.List<Key>>> getNonGraphBeansToPurge()

        Customers should implement this method to return the IDs of beans that are linked to this ABContact but are outside the contact graph. The internal purge logic uses the contact graph to decide what beans are part of the contact, but relies on this method for information about beans outside the graph but that should still be deleted during purge.
